					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Unrelatedly, I strongly recommend using variables instead of immediate addresses for things in RAM. (i.e. add &quot;NMIcount .rs 1&quot; right after &quot;.rsset&quot; and don't use &quot; $1E&quot;)<br /><br />Here's the loop that vegaplay uses to upload a nametable:<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">NameLoop:&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;; loop to draw entire nametable<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; LDA (pointerLo),y<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; STA $2007<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; INY<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; BNE NameLoop<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; INC pointerHi<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; DEX<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; BNE NameLoop</div></div>

