k" href="http://pastebin.com/i8Pnctng">http://pastebin.com/i8Pnctng</a><!-- m --><br /><br />The changes I did:<br />-swapped the palette and attribute tables so that the attributes are loaded during the BgLoop<br />-made the program to initialized the NMI flag before allowing NMIs<br />-disabled NMIs before the BgLoop and enabled them right before the NMI ends</div>

					
